{"tid":571452,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"奧海城間taste出過既壽司薄餅","createTime":"2018-02-24T16:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T11:29:21.000Z","uid":171474,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a6141407762230a7f4114fbc742b21c3d2f6186d","tid":571452,"uid":171474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"之前奧海城二期間taste未摺埋個陣，有個叫壽司薄餅既壽司飯勁好味！有好多魚生鋪係壽司飯面頭，又有好多沙律醬，仲要用槍燒過個面，成個飯超級好味！魚生唔會少，每一淡飯都有魚生，超滿足。<br />\n但自從奧海城間taste摺埋左之後，就唔知邊間taste有呢個壽司薄餅喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人知我講緊咩，如果知道邊間taste有呢個飯，可唔可以話我知？真係好想食番<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f29cc869e720d512a6fccf27761f58fef71cafc","tid":571452,"uid":15230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T17:56:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.tvmost.com.hk/201508232336_article_sp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tvmost.com.hk%2F201508232336_article_sp&d=HfNrgXPymsOIlUf6%2B%2FTneDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=305e381e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.tvmost.com.hk/201508232336_article_sp</a> <br />\n呢隻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dfb57420c69f7e2eb365d877814830e57bcd3bc","tid":571452,"uid":3508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"我中學果時已經係百佳見過有,九龍城果間<br />\n果時好似大約2000年左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28a6fde718025c709205116e6cd07a4bba892df","tid":571452,"uid":156331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T01:54:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c254817f20f2bf6797e12cd2f6fb4fb45bf6bbb","tid":571452,"uid":171474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f29cc869e720d512a6fccf27761f58fef71cafc","tid":571452,"uid":15230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T17:56:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.tvmost.com.hk/201508